  "claim": {
    "summary": "Fix Receipts OpenClaw plugin install blocker",
    "details": "OpenClaw blocked the receipts plugin install because openclaw/plugin.js imported child_process. Reworked the runtime plugin to write receipts in-process with fs/path/crypto plus schema and Markdown modules, removing subprocess execution from the plugin adapter. Documented required hooks.allowConversationAccess=true policy and added tests for the safe writer."
